resource.chars: On the margins of p. 224 are some names in pencil of cent. xiii, and amounts of money, mostly ob. and quart. (0.5 d. or 0.25 d.). Among the entries I can read are

Garinus ob. Iohannes deb. Alicia ... ob. Ferandus ob. Matell vidua ob. Wills sutor quart. Ric bere ob. Walt lutere quart. Nic Eugen quart. (Cri)stina vidua ob. (Iu)dith vidua ob. (S)abina vidua ob. ...a Chantebon ob. ...ditha Carpn ob. (Con)stantia nutrix quart. Jo(h)annes le bon quart. ...as consutrix quart. and de Th////ng ... In lower margin: Summa collecta ad C..t.f. per T. frances per... xxixd ob.
